َّرُونَ","english":"And (the servants of Paradise) will be (roaming about) with fruits which (the ones drawn near) will like,","roots_ordered":["خير","فكه"],"tokens_ordered":["وفاكهة","مما","يتخيرون"],"vec_preview":[-0.10409999638795853,0.0575999990105629,-0.050200000405311584,0.008799999952316284,0.07670000195503235,-0.02449999935925007,-0.03909999877214432,0.07649999856948853]},{"ayah_id":"56:21","surah":56,"ayah":21,"arabic":"وَلَحْمِ طَيْرٍ مِّمَّا يَشْتَهُونَ","english":"And (there will be) bird-meat as well which they (the ones drawn near) will desire.","roots_ordered":["شهو","طير","لحم"],"tokens_ordered":["ولحم","طير","مما","يشتهون"],"vec_preview":[-0.03189999982714653,0.08910000324249268,-0.0754999965429306,0.0544000007212162,0.020600000396370888,-0.06989999860525131,-0.04450000077486038,0.04580000042915344]},{"ayah_id":"56:22","surah":56,"ayah":22,"arabic":"وَحُورٌ عِينٌ","english":"And also (in their companionship will be) maidens with wide lovely eyes,","roots_ordered":["حور","عين"],"tokens_ordered":["وحور","عين"],"vec_preview":[-0.01140000019222498,0.09619999676942825,-0.021299999207258224,0.09109999984502792,0.05779999867081642,-0.11249999701976776,-0.009200000204145908,0.11020000278949738]},{"ayah_id":"56:23","surah":56,"ayah":23,"arabic":"كَأَمْثَالِ اللُّؤْلُؤِ الْمَكْنُونِ","english":"Like pearls kept hidden, well-guarded.","roots_ordered":["كنن","لالا","مثل"],"tokens_ordered":["كامثال","اللءلء","المكنون"],"vec_preview":[-0.04470000043511391,0.07540000230073929,0.003000000026077032,0.014100000262260437,0.045099999755620956,-0.0632999986410141,-0.037700001150369644,0.09269999712705612]},{"ayah_id":"56:24","surah":56,"ayah":24,"arabic":"جَزَاءً بِمَا كَانُوا يَعْمَلُونَ","english":"(That) will be the reward of the (pious) works which they used to do.","roots_ordered":["جزي","عمل","كون"],"tokens_ordered":["جزاء","بما","كانوا","يعملون"],"vec_preview":[-0.04479999840259552,0.04410000145435333,-0.07970000058412552,0.0348999984562397,0.019500000402331352,-